  "name": "Deploy - Magento 2.1 Skylink Connector",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"deploy-magento-2-1-skylink-connector\">Deploy - Magento 2.1 Skylink Connector</h1>\n<p><span><span>This article explains how to deploy a Magento 2.1 Skylink Connector once a signed contract has been received and paid for:</span></span></p>\n<p><span>Enable EDS</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (45).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbnEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to <a href=\"\">MGMT</a></p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>BackOffice &gt; BO Site List</strong></p>\n<p>3. Filter by company name in <strong>Admin Link</strong></p>\n<p>4. Click on <span><strong>Edit</strong></span> and tick <strong>EDS Enabled</strong></p>\n<p>5. Select <strong>Identifier </strong>(Client ID) and copy onto clipboard (Ctrl C)</p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (46).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbsEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Login to clients Retail Express</p>\n<p>2. Navigate to <strong>Quick Links &gt; Web Services Configuration</strong></p>\n<p>3. Set <strong>WebStoreEDS</strong> to enabled</p>\n<p>4. Set <strong>WebStoreV2</strong> to enabled</p>\n<p>5. Save Changes</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>Zendesk - Sending the email </span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"rtaImage (47).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powbxEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>1. Add a new ticket</p>\n<p>2. Add the email address for the contact on the solutions agreement</p>\n<p>3. Select the macro <strong>eCommerce &gt; BYO &gt;</strong> <strong>Skylink BYO Documentation (Magento 2)</strong></p>\n<p>4. Replace the [CLIENT ID] section with the Identifier/Client ID you copied out of MGMT</p>\n<p>5. Submit the ticket as Pending in Skystore Triage Queue (as they need to send back SSH key)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
